Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,5,,开眼 万花筒写轮眼的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管前面的路有多么黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管碰到什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉刚才好像有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上的灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还没到睡觉的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 婶婶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动啊 动啊 动啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万花筒写轮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么哥哥会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了测试我自己的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测试器量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这个 把大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒谎 这不是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以一直扮演你理想中的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了测试你的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将来可能会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我测试器量的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在讨厌我 憎恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直期望能超越我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 我才让你活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是万花筒写轮眼的开眼者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那需要特殊的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉自己最亲密的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于昨晚\N跳入南贺河自杀的宇智波止水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来聚会的另一个人就是止水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像将止水当成自己的亲哥哥对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥杀了止水先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我得到了这种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南贺神社的正殿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右数第七块榻榻米之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是家族的秘密聚会地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面记载着宇智波一族的瞳术为何而生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是其真正的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你开眼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包含我在内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握万花筒写轮眼的就有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有让你活下去的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本没有被杀的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想杀我 就憎恨 怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后丑陋地活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地逃啊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要苟延残喘地活着便好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你拥有和我一样的眼睛时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 据说只有这个孩子得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子好像还有个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说行踪不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到名门宇智波一族会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 要去上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才看到鼬了 真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是一流的忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七岁就以第一名的成绩从忍者学校毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十岁就升为了中忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八岁就会使用写轮眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真是宇智波一族的骄傲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么总是只想着哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是哥哥 你是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸总是很在乎你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南贺神社的正殿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右数第七块榻榻米之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是家族的秘密聚会地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 就是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后去不去点心铺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去 不去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈很和蔼 真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让我妈知道我买零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波一族好像都被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听爸爸说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那家伙活了下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸总是会提到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈说过些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想杀我 就憎恨 怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管前面的路多么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管碰到什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始 我就是一个复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助现在身处黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里停下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就追不上佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙现在身处黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然真想置我于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是你的朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们第七班一直以来所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部毫无意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管碰到什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此 打倒你才有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我没弄懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你真的想置我于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想置我于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在连你刚才说的话是真是假都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许只有我一厢情愿地真正当你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就太没面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
